product_data.product_name: Certain HP Enterprise LaserJet, LaserJet Managed printers

versions.version: See HP Security Bulletin reference for affected versions.

description_data.value: Certain HP Enterprise LaserJet and HP LaserJet Managed Printers are potentially vulnerable to denial of service due to WS-Print request and potential injections of Cross Site Scripting via jQuery-UI.
Certain HP Enterprise LaserJet and HP LaserJet Managed Printers are potentially vulnerable to denial of service due to WS-Print request and potential injections of Cross Site Scripting via jQuery-UI.
